<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Hello all, Ive had a hard time finding decent places to discuss our class. Seems to be a well rounded group here so let me put this to you. Why doesnt anyone that stands up for enchanters lay out their tactics and spell use against creatures or players? The people who complain, if rudely, point out every little detail of the problems they seem to have. But people who think enchanters are great act like they are protecting state secrets, shhhh, its a great class but I cant tell you how or why. Vague generalities about this and that dont cut it. You think we're good, well how so? Site an example. &lt;chuckle&gt; Your not ruining anything by stating what you do, persons reading posts are obviously looking for advice. If they we're worried about discovering your tactics they wouldnt be digging through websites looking for help.<p>

I hear some of you talking about how your encouraged to be grouped and thats how you should hunt. Well unlike maybe yourself or myself, some people have a hard time interacting with groups. Not because of their class or race, but maybe they type slow or are just shy. So some middle ground is a point Id like to make while Im babbling too.<p>

Last quick comment and Ill shut up and let you cut my post up into ribbons, as I can hear someone sharping their set now. I play on a Pvp server. Tallon server. No matter what your view point is on pvp, fact is that some changes in our pets and spells seem VERY MUCH so needed in this server setting. As Im sure they are need else where. So necros and mage's are excellent against some creature in a dungeon eh? Well try having that Dot on yourself! Been there and done it, not much I could do about it. I use my puny DD spell on a necro, he sucks twice the hps right out of me. Whats the answer? Well not to get rid of Charm and fear I scream! I mean give us something here thats an obvious asset to enchanters. You may have a great tactic you use, but if your not sharing it I dont care to hear you tell me how great you are. Theres a reason necro and mage pkers are in greater fay is such records, they know they can get away with it. Im an enchanter and Im an elf, the safest place for me is anywhere but in elven lands.<p>

See ya around. Give a tell if ya see me. Ill be checking back to see people 'comments'. Take care.<p>

Roeth<br>
One elf enchanter<br>
Tallon server.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
